graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    Dashboard -->|CRD management| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Dashboard -->|metrics queries| Thanos[Thanos Querier<br/>openshift-monitoring]
    Dashboard -->|image metadata| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry]

    %% Internal ODH Component Integration
    Dashboard -->|notebook mgmt| Kubeflow[Kubeflow Notebook Controller]
    Dashboard -->|model serving| KServe[KServe Controller]
    Dashboard -->|pipeline data| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines API]
    Dashboard -.->|metadata fetch| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>feature-flagged]

    %% Custom Resources Managed
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io]
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages| AcceleratorProfile[AcceleratorProfile CR<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig CR<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
    Dashboard -->|reads| DataScienceCluster[DataScienceCluster CR<br/>datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io/v1]
    Dashboard -->|reads| DSCInitialization[DSCInitialization CR<br/>dscinitialization.opendatahub.io/v1]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 18+]
    Dashboard -->|framework| Fastify[Fastify 4.16.0]
    Dashboard -->|UI library| PatternFly[PatternFly 5.2.1]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient["kubernetes/client-node 0.12.2"]

    %% Controllers that watch CRs
    NotebookCR -.->|watched by| Kubeflow
    ServingRuntimeCR -.->|watched by| KServe

    %% Integration from other components
    OdhApplicationCatalog[ODH Application Catalog] -->|provides apps| Dashboard
    QuickStarts[Quick Start Tutorials] -->|provides guides| Dashboard

